definitions.definition: Of or relating to naturism , the philosophical belief in a naked, natural life and prefers to live without clothes , often for reasons of health , ecology , religious belief, and/or ethical concerns.
Relating to or believing in the doctrine of naturism , which attributes everything to nature.
